WEBVTT

00:14:27.979 --> 00:14:31.011
We organized the worldwide marches
against child labor

00:14:31.011 --> 00:14:37.073
and that has also resulted in 
a new international convention

00:14:37.073 --> 00:14:41.172
to protect the children
who are in the worst forms.

00:14:42.262 --> 00:14:46.351
And the concrete result was that
the number of child laborers globally

00:14:46.351 --> 00:14:51.891
has gone down by one third 
in the last 15 years.

00:14:51.891 --> 00:14:56.311
(Applause)

00:14:56.311 --> 00:14:59.721
So, in each case,

00:14:59.721 --> 00:15:03.510
it began from anger,